<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241960>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 15. Corethrella borkenti sp. n., male adult. 9. Head, anterior view. 10. Thorax and legs, lateral view. 11. Antenna. 12. Wing. 13. Abdomen, dorsal view. 14. Left gonocoxite and gonostylus, dorsal view. 15. Aedeagus." ;
