<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241961>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 21. Corethrella borkenti sp. n., pupa (16 – 18) and larva (19 – 21). 16. Pupal exuviae, dorsal view. 17. Right respiratory organ. 18. Metathorax and abdomen, tergites to the left, sternites to the right. 19. Larval head capsule, ventral view. 20. Right mandible, dorsal view. 21. Mentum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241961/files/figure.png" ;
